FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784720908
OL,3,CHome Office unlawfully approved
OL,4,Cmilitary site housing asylum seekers,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FThe hearing before Mr Justice Mould is
OL,8,Fdue to conclude on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
